          <declname>Mask</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Clears pending interrupts with the provided mask. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function should be called after the software has serviced the interrupts that are pending. This function will assert if the hardware device has not been built with interrupt capabilities.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
